## üîß Personal Aliases & Shortcuts

### Bash Aliases (add to ~/.bashrc or ~/.zshrc)
```bash
# Project-specific aliases
alias pgadmin='cd ~/PROJECTS/Postgresql'
alias pgup='docker-compose up'
alias pgdown='docker-compose down'
alias pgclean='docker-compose down -v'
alias pglogs='docker-compose logs -f'

# Backend shortcuts
alias pgbe='cd ~/PROJECTS/Postgresql/backend'
alias pgtest='cd ~/PROJECTS/Postgresql/backend && poetry run pytest'
alias pglint='cd ~/PROJECTS/Postgresql/backend && poetry run ruff check .'

# Frontend shortcuts
alias pgfe='cd ~/PROJECTS/Postgresql/frontend'
alias pgdev='cd ~/PROJECTS/Postgresql/frontend && npm run dev'

# Git shortcuts
alias gs='git status'
alias gd='git diff'
alias gl='git log --oneline -10'
alias gp='git push'
```

### Fish Aliases (if you use Fish shell)
```fish
# Add to ~/.config/fish/config.fish
abbr pgadmin 'cd ~/PROJECTS/Postgresql'
abbr pgup 'docker-compose up'
# etc...
```

